==Charters==
Air Koryo operates the following routes as per demand<ref name=autogenerated1>[http://www.airlinequality.com/Forum/koryo.htm Customer reviews on Air Koryo]</ref>:

*'''[[South Korea]]'''
**[[Busan]] - [[Gimhae International Airport]] as (JS801/802 and JS801/802)
**[[Seoul]] - [[Incheon International Airport]] as (JS815/816 and 817/818)
*'''[[Japan]]'''
**[[Nagoya]] - [[Nagoya Airport]] as (JS831/832)
**[[Niigata, Niigata|Niigata]] - [[Niigata Airport]] as (JS831/832)
*'''[[People's Republic of China]]'''
**[[Shenzhen]] - [[Shenzhen Bao'an International Airport]] as (JS137/138)
*'''[[Macau]]''' 
**[[Macau International Airport]]  as (JS187/188)
*'''[[Bulgaria]]'''
**[[Sofia]] - [[Sofia International Airport]] as (JS217/218)
*'''[[Russia]]'''
**[[Moscow]] - [[Sheremetyevo International Airport]] as (JS215/216)
**[[Vladivostok]] - [[Vladivostok International Airport]]
along with limited services to [[Zurich]], [[Prague]], [[Vienna]], [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Budapest]], [[Amsterdam]], [[New York City]]
<br />
<sub>Note these services were operated as additional flights to existing services to destinations operated to and previously operated to</sub>

